title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1220.40 - Leaking, loose, improperly packaged and marked baggage or express not accepted for handling
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1220.40 - Leaking, loose, improperly packaged and marked baggage or express not accepted for handling

State Regulations

No piece of baggage or express will be accepted for
handling at the terminal, if in a leaking or loose condition. No piece of
express will be accepted for handling if it is not properly packaged and
marked. Notes
